{"tid":855512,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"漫威棄將James Gunn倒戈　加盟DC拍《自殺特攻2》","createTime":"2018-10-10T05:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T06:21:14.000Z","uid":212399,"like":70,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7c7850f2ead555c8f217c48c91273551647cb1ef","tid":855512,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181010/photo/bkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181010094442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181010%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181010094442&h=576f76e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJames Gunn傳過檔執導《自殺特攻2》。<br />\n<br />\n為漫威（Marvel）拍下兩集票房大賣超英片《銀河守護隊》（Guardians of the Galaxy）的美國名導演James Gunn，之前因為被翻出多年前社交網的不恰當言論之後即被炒魷冇得拍第3集《銀》。而James昨日被傳「掉轉槍頭」過檔DC開拍超級奸雄片《自殺特攻：超能暴隊2》（Suicide Squad 2），他將會撰寫劇本之餘亦會親自操刀執導！而一直表明立場撐James的《銀》男星「Drax」Dave Bautista亦於社交網留言暗示有意「跳船」，他收到消息後留言說：「邊度可以登記？」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次已非首次漫威超級導演過檔DC，之前《復仇者聯盟》（The Avengers）導演Joss Whedon就接因家事而中途辭拍的Zack Snyder手完成《正義聯盟》（Justice League）。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181010/photo/bkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_02p.jpg?20181010094442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181010%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20181010094442&h=0f71dfca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在《銀》飾演Drax的Dave有意過檔。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181010/photo/bkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_03p.jpg?20181010094442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181010%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20181010094442&h=8e54baed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDave（右）一直支持James。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181010/photo/bkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_04p.jpg?20181010094442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181010%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181010090107890-1010_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20181010094442&h=bf4c8d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《自》2016年上映時成績麻麻。<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://goo.gl/fbu2Yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Ffbu2Yo&d=vnaf3LLGtUYd2jTxRifVD%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=94a90f6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/fbu2Yo</a><br />\n唔通Marvel真係係復仇者聯盟4之後走下坡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24d81b0946b7e4a2fc7dd10ab0a97237620ff02","tid":855512,"uid":61271,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"Marvel走下坡都唔等如DC可以翻身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5f0148e029cc0c1a56b75235ebb5a7badb2baa","tid":855512,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"Oh James Gunn mola mola"},{"pid":"c60cc4cc9d9affeb19de93cbe5d48628b7860e25","tid":855512,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"佢倒戈我唔愕然，但講到Dave都走去跟James我就愕然"},{"pid":"b1d88294491d36c356e8854cae1cb8eb3768231f","tid":855512,"uid":212399,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:25:03.000Z","msg":"自殺特攻或者DC翻唔翻到身唔係最重要<br />\n反而想知道銀河守護隊3邊個導演拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe7511a4671ca67467c776f8167661ad6f2b657","tid":855512,"uid":77692,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b1d88294491d36c356e8854cae1cb8eb3768231f","tid":855512,"uid":212399,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:25:03.000Z","msg":"自殺特攻或者DC翻唔翻到身唔係最重要<br />\n反而想知道銀河守護隊3邊個導演拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"好似傳過話雷神